  "helpTitle": "Help & Support",
  "helpSearchHint": "Search for help topics...",
  "helpCategoryReading": "Reading",
  "helpCategoryWriting": "Writing",
  "helpCategoryDiscovery": "Discovery",
  "helpCategoryCommunity": "Community",
  "helpCategoryAccount": "Account",
  "helpCategoryCollaboration": "Collaboration",
  "faqCustomizeReaderQ": "How do I customize the reader?",
  "faqCustomizeReaderA": "Open any book and tap the 'Aa' icon in the top toolbar. You can change the font size, switch between Serif and Sans fonts, and choose a theme (Light, Sepia, or Dark).",
  "faqOfflineReadingQ": "Can I read books offline?",
  "faqOfflineReadingA": "Yes! Tap the download icon on the book details page. Once downloaded, you can access the book from your 'Saved' tab even without an internet connection.",
  "faqBookmarksQ": "How do bookmarks work?",
  "faqBookmarksA": "Wreadom automatically saves your progress as you read. To manually mark a specific spot, tap the bookmark icon in the reader's top toolbar.",
  "faqQuoteCommentQ": "What is 'Quote & Comment'?",
  "faqQuoteCommentA": "Highlight any text in a book to see the selection menu. You can 'Quote & Comment' to share your thoughts on a specific passage with the community.",
  "faqStartStoryQ": "How do I start a new story?",
  "faqStartStoryA": "Go to the 'Writer Dashboard' from your profile menu and tap the 'Add' icon. This will open the Writer Pad where you can start drafting your first chapter.",
  "faqAutoSaveQ": "Is there an auto-save feature?",
  "faqAutoSaveA": "Yes, the Writer Pad automatically saves your drafts every 10 seconds. You can see the 'Last Saved' status at the top of the editor.",
  "faqPublishWorkQ": "How do I publish my work?",
  "faqPublishWorkA": "Once your story is ready, tap 'Publish' in the Writer Pad. You'll be asked to provide a title, synopsis, and relevant topics before it goes live for the community.",
  "faqOrganizeChaptersQ": "Can I organize chapters?",
  "faqOrganizeChaptersA": "Absolutely! Use the chapter menu (list icon) in the editor to add new chapters, switch between them, or reorder your story structure.",
  "faqCollaborationQ": "How do collaborations work?",
  "faqCollaborationA": "In the Writer Pad, enable Collaboration and choose a user you follow as a co-author. They receive a request, and once accepted, both authors can edit the content and appear together on the book page.",
  "faqFindBooksQ": "How do I find new books?",
  "faqFindBooksA": "Use the 'Discover' tab to browse by trending genres like Fantasy, Romance, and Sci-Fi. You can also search specifically for titles or authors.",
  "faqOriginalsQ": "What are 'Originals'?",
  "faqOriginalsA": "Originals are stories written and published directly by authors within the Wreadom community.",
  "faqInternetArchiveQ": "What is the Internet Archive integration?",
  "faqInternetArchiveA": "Wreadom connects to the Internet Archive to give you access to millions of classic books and public domain works alongside community originals.",
  "faqDailyTopicQ": "What is the Daily Topic?",
  "faqDailyTopicA": "Every day, Wreadom features a new writing or discussion prompt. Tap the banner on the Home feed to participate and see what others are sharing.",
  "faqFollowAuthorQ": "How do I follow an author?",
  "faqFollowAuthorA": "Tap on an author's name or avatar to visit their public profile, then tap 'Follow' to see their latest posts and story updates in your feed.",
  "faqMessagingQ": "Can I message other users?",
  "faqMessagingA": "Yes, you can start direct conversations with other users. Visit their profile or use the 'Messages' icon on your navigation bar to manage your chats.",
  "faqChangeThemeQ": "How do I change the app theme?",
  "faqChangeThemeA": "Go to Profile -> Menu (top-right) -> Theme. You can choose between Light, Dark, or System default modes.",
  "faqUpdateProfileQ": "How do I update my profile?",
  "faqUpdateProfileA": "In the 'Edit Profile' section of your settings, you can update your display name, pen name, and bio.",
  "faqNotificationsQ": "Where are my notifications?",
  "faqNotificationsA": "Tap the bell icon on the home screen or profile to see updates about likes, comments, and new followers.",
  "faqChangeLanguageQ": "How do I change the app language?",
  "faqChangeLanguageA": "Go to Settings -> Language to switch between English and Hindi.",
  "faqWhatAreReadsQ": "What are 'Reads'?",
  "faqWhatAreReadsA": "Reads indicate how many times a story has been viewed. It updates automatically as the community explores your work.",
  "faqTapToSeekQ": "How does tap-to-seek work in Read Aloud?",
  "faqTapToSeekA": "While 'Read Aloud' is active, simply tap on any paragraph to jump the voice directly to that section.",
  "faqShareQuoteImageQ": "Can I share quotes as images?",
  "faqShareQuoteImageA": "Yes! Highlight any text and choose 'Share Quote' to create a beautiful, shareable image of that passage.",
  "faqReportContentQ": "How do I report inappropriate content?",
  "faqReportContentA": "Tap the three-dot menu on any post, comment, or book and select 'Report'. Our team will review it promptly.",
  "faqPinUnpinQ": "Can I pin my favorite comments?",
  "faqPinUnpinA": "Yes! If you are the author of a post, you can pin a comment to the top of the discussion by tapping the 'Pin' option in its menu.",
  "faqMessagingRulesQ": "Are there rules for messaging?",
  "faqMessagingRulesA": "To prevent spam, you can only send one message to a new contact. Once they reply, you can chat freely.",
  "faqDailyTopicsParticipationQ": "How do I participate in Daily Topics?",
  "faqDailyTopicsParticipationA": "Tap the Daily Topic banner on your home feed. You can read submissions or add your own response to the prompt.",
  "faqFeedUpdatesQ": "What shows up in my Feed?",
  "faqFeedUpdatesA": "Your Feed is a personalized stream of updates from authors you follow, including new posts, reviews, and story chapters.",
  "faqMultiChapterWriterQ": "Can I write multiple chapters at once?",
  "faqMultiChapterWriterA": "Yes! In the Writer Pad, use the chapters list to create multiple segments of your story. You can save them all as a single draft before publishing.",
  "faqProfilePicturesQ": "How do I update my profile and cover images?",
  "faqProfilePicturesA": "Visit your profile and tap on the camera icons on your avatar or cover photo to upload new images from your device.",
